{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_01","textHome":"再次自我介绍，我是环彩羽。@平时在官方宣传漫画「魔法☆报告」里，@和小圆前辈一起为大家传达魔法纪录的情报！@这次以4星的身份登场了！是4星哦！@难得出场，请为了抽到我而努力吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"id":120100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":401}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_17","textHome":"可以带3个记忆结晶了……@嗯，真难选……@虽然小圆前辈的记忆也不错……@但还是这个吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":120100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_18","textHome":"记忆结晶换好了！@话说，那边绑着两条缎带的粉毛是谁？@颜色跟我重了吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":120100,"motion":201}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_19","textHome":"感谢你在我身上使用了贵重的素材！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_20","textHome":"我要顶替小圆前辈进支援栏了，因为是4星！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_21","textHome":"因为作为4星实装了，@这段声音应该可以在档案功能里听到。@来自魔法报告的我是4星！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_22","textHome":"终于……终于！心心念念的5星！@感谢培养我到现在！@今后也请多指教5星的我……@小圆前辈说……@「目前的情况充满了死亡flag的气息」……@别、别说这种话啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.9,"chara":[{"id":120100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":120100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":401}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_23","textHome":"你好，我是越过了小圆前辈立起的@死亡flag，成为了6星的环彩羽！@这6颗星真是耀眼啊。就从这些星星里，@放出把敌人一扫而空的光束……@我大概做不到，不过小圆前辈的话……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_24","textHome":"久等了！今天是刷副本？@还是解任务？还是要推主线？@对，来到这个世界的我很努力！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_25","textHome":"早上好！早起是三文之德，@说不定现在能抽到4星魔法少女呢……@啊啊啊啊啊啊！？是2星记忆结晶的山！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":300,"tear":1}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_26","textHome":"最近，午饭经常和先实装的小圆前辈一起@去推荐的拉面店。要一起去吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":120100,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_02","textHome":"初次见面，我是从「魔法☆报告」的世界过来@的环彩羽。虽然这里已经有我了，但来自魔@法报告的我也请多关照啦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"id":120100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_27","textHome":"天黑了呢。@趁还不晚，回魔法报告的世界去好了……@到了该准备晚饭的时间了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":120100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_28","textHome":"深夜了，有件很恐怖的事情……@不知道为什么，我的账号就没钻了……@连菲莉希亚也是……好可怕……@呜呜……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.1,"chara":[{"id":120100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":120100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":120100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":120100,"tear":1}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_29","textHome":"刷副本是很重要的。@不仅能得到素材，完成任务还能获得魔法石！@有时间的话多刷点吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_30","textHome":"可以去打关卡了吧？AP满了就浪费了……@不是，不能放着魔女不管才对。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":120100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":120100}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_31","textHome":"小圆前辈拜托我传播纸相扑……@是说魔法报告式的镜层。@纸相扑用的小人我已经准备好了，@请拿去用吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"id":120100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_32","textHome":"好多魔法少女……@诶？魔法报告的魔法少女@跟魔法纪录的魔法少女混在一起了……？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_33","textHome":"说起来，FM神滨重新开张了没？@嗯，大概小圆前辈又忘了吧？@下次去问问好了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_34","textHome":"啊呜啊呜……哇，就算偷袭我，@也不会掉小番茄的哦。@我已经和小圆前辈都吃完了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":201}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_35","textHome":"有空的话来玩玛吉斯游戏吧。@就像狼人游戏一样。那么，谁是玛吉斯呢！？@哈？又是「非洲人」！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_023.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":201}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_36","textHome":"小圆前辈好像……趁着我变大的时候，@混在别的东西里偷看我……@诶！？偷看什么？@这、这我不太方便说……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":401}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":300}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_03","textHome":"这么说来，还是魔法报告先开始第二部了呢。"}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_37","textHome":"两边的八千代，虽然画风不一样，@但都是美人呢……还有……@连擅长说教也是一模一样……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_38","textHome":"魔法报告的万万岁和魔法纪录的是一样的口味@我感觉有点太浓了些……@分数？呃，50分吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":120100,"motion":201}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_39","textHome":"好像快下雨了。要是忘了带伞……@就一起进来吧？莎奈把盾借给我当伞了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_40","textHome":"这边的菲莉希亚，牙不是那样尖尖的呢……@那样的也很可爱哦。@就是把手放进去会被咬而已。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":401}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_41","textHome":"只踩着白条过人行道……@嗯哼，我做到了……@啊啊！？难道被看到了！？@忘、忘了这件事吧！"}]},{